name: smardex
UserFees_info:
A minor fee is collected on each swap, functioning as trading fees.
The fees are set at 0.07% on Ethereum and 0.1% on other chains.
On other networks, fees may vary between different pairs and chains.
Refer to https://docs.smardex.io/overview/what-is-smardex/fees for detailed information.
Fees_info:
A minor fee is collected on each swap, functioning as trading fees.
The fees are set at 0.07% on Ethereum and 0.1% on other chains.
On other networks, fees may vary between different pairs and chains.
Refer to https://docs.smardex.io/overview/what-is-smardex/fees for detailed information.
Revenue_info: 0.02% of each swap on Ethereum is collected for staking pool (SDEX holders that staked). On other chains, fees are collected for liquidity providers and fees may vary between different pairs and chains. Refer to https://docs.smardex.io/overview/what-is-smardex/fees for detailed information.
HoldersRevenue_info: 0.02% of each swap on Ethereum is collected for staking pool (SDEX holders that staked). On other chains staking is not available and fees are collected for buybacks SDEX and burns.
SupplySideRevenue_info: 0.05% of each swap on Ethereum is collected for liquidity providers. On other chains, fees collected for liquidity providers and fees may vary between different pairs and chains. Refer to https://docs.smardex.io/overview/what-is-smardex/fees for detailed information.
